      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This vehicle is ready for some TLC and a fresh start! While it shows significant wear and will need some mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back to its best, it's a fantastic opportunity for a handy owner or someone looking for a budget-friendly entry into car restoration. It has plenty of character and is waiting for someone to bring it back to life!",
